digiKam 1.3.0 - Release date: 2010-06-07

NEW FEATURES:

General        : New Database interface to support different database backend.
                 MySql and SQlite are supported. Internal and Remote MySql server are supported.
General        : RawEngine dependency set to 1.1.0 version.
General        : MetadataEngine dependency set to 1.1.0 version.
AdvancedRename : New option: database. Allows to rename files according to database values.
QueueManager   : Add capability to apply an image waterwark over a photo.
General        : MetadatEngine dependency set to 1.1.0 release.
General        : RawEngine dependency set to 1.1.0 release.
DNGWriter   : Update Adobe DNG sdk to 1.3.0.
                 Support non-square pixels.
                 Support 4-color sensors.
                 Support Fuji-sensors (experimental).
SmugExport     : Support export of Captions.

